The Techno Fantasy Atlas for Fabula Ultima will guide you into high tech, dystopian
worlds, where outcast heroes fifi ght inequality while merciless villains commit any
atrocity to safeguard their privilege. Restore hope to these lands ruled by corruption,
as the most famous JRPG resistance movements did before you!
