» EXAMPLE: THE GLADSHEIMR
And now, here’s a sample group vehicle: the Gladsheimr is the starship led by
Commander Skadi (see page 99). It is an interstellar ship (see page 79) of large size,
obtained through the Stolen Transport Quirk (see page 127).
