HOPLOSPHERE
d66 Name Effect (while the item is equipped)
16 Cyclonic
You gain Resistance to air damage. If this item is a weapon, all
damage it deals becomes air.
u Coag. 2: You gain Immunity to air damage.
u Coag. 3: Any air damage you deal ignores Resistances. When
you deal damage, you may change its type to air.
21 Dark
You gain Resistance to dark damage. If this item is a weapon,
all damage it deals becomes dark.
u Coag. 2: You gain Immunity to dark damage.
u Coag. 3: Any dark damage you deal ignores Resistances.
When you deal damage, you may change its type to dark.
22 Dazing* Each target hit by this weapon suffers dazed.
This hoplosphere occupies 2 slots.
