You’re Done When I Say So w When a creature that Vyne can see reaches 0 Hit Points, if
that creature is not suffering from the shaken status effect, she immediately performs a free
attack against that creature with her Shock Baton. If the attack hits, it deals no damage and
the target cannot Surrender nor Sacrifice: instead, they recover 20 Hit Points and suffer the
dazed and shaken status effects.
