SPELLS
h In Corpore Sano w 30 MP × T w Up to three creatures w Instantaneous.
Each target recovers 40 Hit Points and recovers from all status effects.
SPECIAL RULES
Outrageous! w After a creature hits the Right Hand with an attack or offensive spell (r), the
Left Hand performs Ipse Dixit against that creature (after that attack or spell has been resolved).
“I am but a humble conduit of the universal will.
